🔥 Arrays (Most Frequent)

Two Sum → use a hash map for O(n)
Product of array except self → prefix/suffix products
Move zeros to end → two-pointer in-place
Merge intervals → sort by start, merge overlaps
Subarray with given sum → sliding window


🔤 Strings

Check if a string is a palindrome → two pointers (left & right)
Longest substring without repeating characters
Anagram check → frequency count or sort
Reverse words in a sentence → split, reverse, join
Longest palindromic substring → expand around center


🔗 Linked Lists

Reverse a linked list
Detect a cycle → Floyd's algorithm (fast/slow pointers)
Find middle of a linked list


🌳 Trees & Graphs

Level order traversal (BFS)
Check if a binary tree is balanced
Find height of a tree


🧮 Math / Logic

Find HCF/GCD of two numbers
Find second highest salary (SQL)
Minimum moves to reach a value

